## Environment Variables

| Variable | Description | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `PORT` | Server port | `3000` |
| `PG_HOST` | PostgreSQL host | `localhost` |
| `PG_PORT` | PostgreSQL port | `5432` |
| `PG_DATABASE` | Database name | `taskmanager` |
| `PG_USER` | DB username | `postgres` |
| `PG_PASSWORD` | DB password | `yourpassword` |
| `MONGO_URI` | MongoDB connection string | `mongodb://localhost:27017/taskmanager` |
| `JWT_SECRET` | Secret for signing tokens | `your_secret_key` |
| `JWT_EXPIRES_IN` | Token expiry (Node.js) | `7d` |
| `JWT_EXPIRES_MINUTES` | Token expiry in minutes (FastAPI) | `10080` |

